0-31T18:08:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98f9e0f0e2f3752ec53404ee7375ed9761597e4e","tid":1682932,"uid":256014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T07:34:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">　　樓主，父母</span><span style=\"color: violet;\">思想</span>難以改變，<span style=\"color: red;\">尤得</span><span style=\"color: green;\">他們，</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">　　講講</span><span style=\"color: green;\">自己家裏</span><span style=\"color: red;\">形勢，</span>不以顏色分類，<span style=\"color: brown;\">以</span><span style=\"color: red;\">支持</span><span style=\"color: green;\">年輕人／</span><span style=\"color: red;\">支持</span>黑警<span style=\"color: red;\">分類，</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">　　爸</span><span style=\"color: red;\">（出生</span><span style=\"color: green;\">國內，</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">因</span><span style=\"color: green;\">國共</span>內戰，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">小時候</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">跟</span><span style=\"color: green;\">爺</span><span style=\"color: violet;\">來到</span><span style=\"color: green;\">香港），他</span><span style=\"color: red;\">支持</span><span style=\"color: green;\">年輕人，他</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">是</span><span style=\"color: green;\">選民，他</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">每次</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">都</span><span style=\"color: red;\">投</span><span style=\"color: green;\">泛民，<br />\n<br />\n　　媽</span><span style=\"color: red;\">（出生</span><span style=\"color: green;\">香港），</span><span style=\"color: green;\">她</span><span style=\"color: red;\">支持</span>黑警，<span style=\"color: green;\">她</span>不是選民，<span style=\"color: green;\">她</span><span style=\"color: violet;\">拿過</span><span style=\"color: green;\">民建聯</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">之</span><span style=\"color: red;\">禮物，</span><span style=\"color: green;\">她</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">覺得</span><span style=\"color: green;\">人家</span><span style=\"color: red;\">做得好，</span><span style=\"color: green;\">她</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">經常</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">於</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">電視機</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">旁</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">話</span><span style=\"color: green;\">年輕人，</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">因為</span><span style=\"color: green;\">年輕人</span><span style=\"color: red;\">幫緊</span><span style=\"color: green;\">我們（爸</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">都</span><span style=\"color: violet;\">知），</span><span style=\"color: green;\">哥</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">和</span><span style=\"color: green;\">我</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">都</span>忍不住<span style=\"color: orange;\">話</span><span style=\"color: green;\">媽，哥</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">話</span><span style=\"color: green;\">媽</span><span style=\"color: red;\">上咗岸，</span><span style=\"color: green;\">我</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">話</span><span style=\"color: green;\">媽</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">「賭馬</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">就</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">賭馬，</span><span style=\"color: red;\">出咩嘢聲，</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">２０４７，</span><span style=\"color: green;\">妳</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">都</span>化灰」<span style=\"color: green;\">（媽</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">有</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">賭馬</span><span style=\"color: red;\">習慣），</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">如果</span>不是<span style=\"color: green;\">自己媽，我</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">會</span><span style=\"color: violet;\">攞</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">支</span>黑色噴漆<span style=\"color: violet;\">幫</span><span style=\"color: green;\">她</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">化妝，</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">　　哥、我、弟、妹</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">於</span><span style=\"color: green;\">香港</span><span style=\"color: red;\">出生，</span><span style=\"color: violet;\">受</span><span style=\"color: green;\">香港教育，哥、我、弟</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">是</span><span style=\"color: green;\">選民，妹</span>不是<span style=\"color: green;\">選民，她</span>除了<span style=\"color: green;\">自己</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">個</span><span style=\"color: green;\">女，</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">其他</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">嘢</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">都好似</span>不關她事，<br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">　　哥</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">是</span><span style=\"color: green;\">教師，知識份子，他</span><span style=\"color: red;\">出過去</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">遊行，</span><span style=\"color: green;\">他</span><span style=\"color: red;\">支持</span><span style=\"color: green;\">年輕人，他</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">每次</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">都</span><span style=\"color: red;\">投</span>泛民，<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">　　我</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">向來</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">是</span><span style=\"color: red;\">支持彩虹，</span>無人權，無彩虹，<span style=\"color: red;\">變相支持</span><span style=\"color: green;\">年輕人，我</span><span style=\"color: red;\">出過去</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">遊行，</span><span style=\"color: green;\">我</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">每次</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">都</span><span style=\"color: red;\">投</span><span style=\"color: green;\">泛民，<br />\n　　弟</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">原本</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">是</span><span style=\"color: red;\">投</span><span style=\"color: green;\">泛民，他</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">於</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">２０１６</span><span style=\"color: red;\">突然開始變了投</span><span style=\"color: green;\">建制。</span><br />\n</strong></span>"}]}